re going... to make cookies... That might... be kind of... interesting.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event23-01-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Really? Why would you have interest in that?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event23-01-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"Snacks like cookies... are easier to grab... and eat when... you're in the middle... of playing games...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event23-01-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"I see... Sounds like the kind of reason you'd give.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event23-01-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"I-I'm... always looking forward... to eating the cookies... that Imai-san makes for us... during my gaming... sessions...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event23-01-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"(... Intriguing. To think Shirokane-san would seem so happy about something... That must mean she's really taken a liking to Imai-san's cookies.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event23-01-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"(Though, I have been thinking about how her treats have a calming effect on people.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event23-01-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"(I'm certain her personality contributes to this as well, but her treats always put the band in a positive mood...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event23-01-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"Hikawa... san...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event23-01-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"(... I wonder if I have what it takes to make something like that. If I could, I'm sure Roselia would benefit...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event23-01-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"Uhm... Hikawa-san...? I-is something wrong...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"odoodo02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event23-01-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Ah... No, nothing at all.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event23-01-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"More importantly, it's getting dark. Let's get home.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event23-01-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"O-okay...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event23-01-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"Uhmmm~, so these ingredients go in this container, and this goes in here...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event23-01-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"Alright, everything is ready!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event23-01-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"... Phew, the day is almost here. Supposedly, there were people who registered right before the deadline too. Seems like this idea was a lot more popular than I expected...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"ando01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event23-01-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"I was all excited before when I said I would do it, but I don't know if I actually can... I'm feeling kind of unsure...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event23-01-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"... Wait, no! I can't count myself out before I even try! You have to always give 100 percent, no matter what you're faced with!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event23-01-039","volume":1}],"speed":0